#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.26"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.26:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.26:0.2"
msgid "3. Uruvelavagga "
msgstr "3. At Uruvelā "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: kuhakasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.26:0.3"
msgid "26. Kuhasutta "
msgstr "26. Deceivers "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.26:1.1"
msgid "“Ye te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū kuhā thaddhā lapā siṅgī unnaḷā asamāhitā, na me te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū māmakā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, those mendicants who are deceivers, stubborn, flatterers, frauds, insolent, and scattered: they are no mendicants of mine. "

msgctxt "an4.26:1.2"
msgid "Apagatā ca te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū imasmā dhammavinayā, na ca te imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ viruḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjanti. "
msgstr "They’ve left this teaching and training, and they don’t achieve growth, improvement, or maturity in this teaching and training. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.26:1.3"
msgid "Ye ca kho te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū nikkuhā nillapā dhīrā atthaddhā susamāhitā, te kho me, bhikkhave, bhikkhū māmakā. "
msgstr "But those mendicants who are genuine, not flatterers, wise, amenable, and serene: they are mendicants of mine. "

msgctxt "an4.26:1.4"
msgid "Anapagatā ca te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū imasmā dhammavinayā. "
msgstr "They haven’t left this teaching and training, "

msgctxt "an4.26:1.5"
msgid "Te ca imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ viruḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjantīti. "
msgstr "and they achieve growth, improvement, or maturity in this teaching and training. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.26:2.1"
msgid "Kuhā thaddhā lapā siṅgī, "
msgstr "Those who are deceivers, stubborn, flatterers, and frauds, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.26:2.2"
msgid "unnaḷā asamāhitā; "
msgstr "insolent and scattered: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.26:2.3"
msgid "Na te dhamme virūhanti, "
msgstr "these don’t grow in the teaching "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.26:2.4"
msgid "sammāsambuddhadesite. "
msgstr "that was taught by the perfected Buddha. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.26:3.1"
msgid "Nikkuhā nillapā dhīrā, "
msgstr "But those who are genuine, not flatterers, wise, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.26:3.2"
msgid "atthaddhā susamāhitā; "
msgstr "amenable, and serene: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.26:3.3"
msgid "Te ve dhamme virūhanti, "
msgstr "these do grow in the teaching "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.26:3.4"
msgid "sammāsambuddhadesite”ti. "
msgstr "that was taught by the perfected Buddha.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.26:3.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
